FightClub.framework
===================

Introduction
------------
FightClub is a framework for connecting to Hellanzb servers, written in Objective-C. It works on the Mac and iPhone.

Adding FightClub
----------------
The easiest way to use FightClub is just to add the .h and .m files to your project. In the future, FightClub will be able to be built standalone into a .framework file on Mac, and .a file for iPhone.